repository-code: "https://github.com/GSLab2025/RSGA"
url: "https://github.com/GSLab2025/RSGA"
abstract: >-
  Core reference implementation of Reciprocal Space Gated Attention (RSGA),
  a method for introducing periodic reciprocal-space long-range corrections
  into short-range local models, with a pointer to the integrated
  GSLab2025/MACE_RSGA variant.
keywords:
  - reciprocal-space gated attention
  - gated linear attention
  - long-range interactions
  - machine learning interatomic potentials
  - MACE
  - periodic systems
